ZH: 我步入了餐厅，准备享用美食。
EN: I walked into the restaurant, ready to enjoy a delicious meal.

ZH: 他步入了漂亮的花园，感受自然的美丽。
EN: He stepped into the beautiful garden, feeling the beauty of nature.

ZH: 她步入了商店，看到了一件很漂亮的裙子。
EN: She entered the store and saw a very pretty dress.

