EN: We stepped into the new year, hoping to achieve better results.

ZH: 你终于步入了大学，开始了新的生活阶段。
EN: You finally entered university and began a new stage of life.

ZH: 他们步入了困境，却依然坚持不懈。
EN: They walked into trouble but still persevered.

ZH: 我们要步入正确的轨道，才能实现我们的目标。
EN: We need to walk on the right track to achieve our goals.

ZH: 她步入了房间，看到了一个惊喜。
EN: She walked into the room and saw a surprise.

ZH: 随着年龄的增长，他步入了中年。
EN: With age, he entered middle age.

ZH: 在大雨中，他们步入了一个避难所，躲避恶劣的天气。
EN: In heavy rain, they walked into a shelter to escape the bad weather.

ZH: 公司步入了新的阶段，需要更多的工作人员。
EN: The company stepped into a new phase and needed more employees.

